vim /etc/nginx/sites-enabled/default
server {
        root /usr/share/nginx/www;
        }
debian jessie 上 #root /var/www/html;
设置nginx的根目录,如果不设置这个根目录，nginx就不知道去哪找文件

http://stackoverflow.com/questions/10674867/nginx-default-public-www-location

Run the command  nginx -V and look for the --prefix. Use that entry to locate your default paths.
the --prefix value is the answer to the question
------------------------------------------------------------------------

find /usr/share/nginx/www -type d -exec chmod 755 {} ; 
find /usr/share/nginx/www -type f -exec chmod 644 {} ; 
chown -R www-data:www-data /usr/share/nginx/www/

###chmod 3755 /usr/share/nginx/www/ 千万不要这么做!设set gid和set bit之后任意用户都能在这个位置创建文件

/usr/share/nginx/www/这个nginx根目录里面的文件夹设权限为755, 文件设权限为644, 
文件属于www-data组的www-data

https://www.v2ex.com/t/169771

----------------------------------------------------------------------------

/etc/nginx/nginx.conf

user www-data www-data; 以www-data账户运行nginx而非root

-----------------------------------------------------------------
or run it in chroot environment!

https://wiki.archlinux.org/index.php/Nginx

https://www.linode.com/docs/websites/nginx/how-to-configure-nginx/

/etc/nginx/sites-available/example.com
location / {}
location /images/ {}    就是example.com/images/

/etc/nginx/sites-available/example.com
location / {
        root /usr/sharg/nginx/what-you-want
        index index.html
}  指定example.com的root location(不明白与sites-enabled/default里server段的root有关系没?)
难道是为同一ip的多域名做的不同根目录?

----------------------------------------------
debian系有sites-enabled和sites-available, enabled是当前启用的，available包含所有的甚至不启用的

https://www.v2ex.com/t/168135
